items.name: ACCESSIBILITY_SETTING_EXPANDED_TEXT
items.purpose: Stores the value (true/false) of the Expanded Text accessibility menu setting to remember a guest user's choice. Preferences.

items.name: ACCESSIBILITY_SETTING_INCREASED_TEXT_SPACING
items.purpose: Stores the value (true/false) of the Increased Text Spacing accessibility menu setting to remember a guest user's choice. Preferences.

items.name: ACCESSIBILITY_SETTING_REDUCED_MOTION
items.purpose: Stores the value (true/false) of the Reduced Motion accessibility menu setting to remember a guest user's choice. Preferences.

items.name: ACCESSIBILITY_SETTING_UNDERLINED_LINKS1
items.purpose: Stores the value (true/false) of the Underlined Links accessibility menu setting to remember a guest user's choice. Preferences.

items.name: COMMERCE_COMPARE_cpDefinitionIds_commerceChannelGroupId
items.purpose: Stores the product's IDs appended to the channel ID for comparing products. Preferences.

items.name: GUEST_LANGUAGE_ID
items.purpose: Stores the preferred language ID to use when the user's language ID is not available to display content in the appropriate language. Preferences.

items.name: LOGIN
items.purpose: Stores the user's id, screen name, or email address depending on the configured authentication type for 'remember me' login. Preferences.

items.name: OAUTH2_REMEMBER_DEVICE_
items.purpose: Stores the authorization grant of a registered OAuth2 application to skip the authorization flow from a previously authorized device. Preferences.

items.name: PASSWORD
items.purpose: Stores the encrypted user password to identify a previously logged in user. Preferences.

items.name: REMEMBER_ME
items.purpose: Stores the end user's 'remember me' preference (true/false). Preferences.

items.name: SAML_SP_SESSION_KEY
items.purpose: Stores a randomly generated string for keeping the SAML Service Provider session alive and allowing it to participate in SAML SLO (Single Log Out). Preferences.

items.name: SAML_SSO_SESSION_ID
items.purpose: Stores the session ID for the user to stay logged in with the SAML Identity Provider. Preferences.

items.name: SELECTED_CATEGORIES_COOKIE_
items.purpose: Stores the selected categories for facilitating adding more than 400 categories in the categories selector popup. Preferences.

items.name: _com_liferay_portal_search_admin_web_portlet_SearchAdminPortlet_userID_hideReindexConfirmationModal
items.purpose: Stores the value (true/false) of the user's decision whether to hide the reindex confirmation dialog permanently. Preferences.

items.name: com.liferay.commerce.wish.list.model.CommerceWishList#groupId
items.purpose: Stores a wishlist ID appended with the group ID to link them to the account the guest creates later. Preferences.

items.name: com.liferay.search.experiences.web_addSXPElementSidebar
items.purpose: Stores the open/close state of the Add Query Elements sidebar in Search Blueprints for the user's convenience. Preferences.

items.name: liferay.cookie.consent
items.purpose: Stores the end user's consent option (true/false) for the use of cookies. Preferences.

items.name: maintenanceSeen
items.purpose: Stores whether the user has frequently dismissed the server maintenance message (true/false) so Analytics Cloud stops displaying it. Preferences.

items.name: sidebar
items.purpose: Stores the open/close state of the Analytics Cloud sidebar for the user's convenience. Preferences.

items.name: userTokenName
items.purpose: Stores a unique token to maintain the user session while using token based Single Sign-On. Functional.
